[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Figure 1: [bold]Regional GVA (bubble size), GVA growth and GVA per capita[bold] (axes intersect at UK average)[bold]&#xa0;
